## How This Works

This blog is automatically generated by analyzing:
1. Git commits and diffs across `~/git/` repositories
2. Claude Code conversation history

Topics remain "open" while actively developing, then get "closed" when complete.

### Commands

- `/auto-tech-blog` - Analyze last 7 days (default)
- `/auto-tech-blog 3` - Analyze last 3 days
- `/auto-tech-blog 14` - Analyze last 2 weeks
